{"tid":472921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：反對政治帶入學校　直播李飛演講？楊稱是教育：給機會港生聽","createTime":"2017-11-18T16:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T15:17:24.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c6382e2d2bb93bd0e4dc03103ff87b58322d256","tid":472921,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄於商台節目表示，愈來愈多人想把政治帶入校園，但他強調，「非常反對把政治帶入學校，影響學生」，認為是「不要得」行為，對教學無好處。<br />\n<br />\n至於教育局鼓勵學校直播基本法委員會主任李飛演講，是否「政治」舉動，楊潤雄稱「（李飛演講）當然是教育（舉動）」。他解釋，李飛是「《基本法》權威」，「有知識及背景講基本法看法」，且對香港市民重要，故「給予機會香港學生聽」，強調「與政治無關」，「對基本法認識，無論政治看法如何，都有責任認識基本法內容」。<br />\n<br />\n問到有學生聽不懂李飛演講內容或「恰眼瞓」等，楊潤雄指，「成個香港一樣，就算全香港一齊聽，都不是所有香港人聽得到全部及掌握到（李飛）說什麼」，但他形容學習是一步步進行，「作為教育局，最重要是提供機會」。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄亦提到近日有學生在校門派發「港獨」單張，重申「港獨」違反《基本法》，「不應該在香港」，討論亦無意義，「香港作為國家一部分是既定事實，應接受事實」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171118/s00001/1510971642877\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171118%2Fs00001%2F1510971642877&d=yxrIo4T3sg0dtfJjKHS33cPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0fcc97d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171118%2Fs00001%2F1510971642877&h=707a6b7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171118/s00001/1510971642877</a>"},{"pid":"c931eb5235d3b4d9de36a88ba0a040c1e5f48f26","tid":472921,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thu